Contact Us
Thunder By The Bay
2025-09-04T14:45:12+00:00
If you have questions on purchasing or purchased tickets, please email support@showslinger.com or call 904-701-4466.
Please Note:
No Tents Or Staked Umbrellas Allowed
No Pets Allowed – Service Animals ONLY
All bands, including featured headliners, are included with the all ticket levels
Parking is free
No Coolers or outside food or beverages permitted
No Refunds
Re-Entry With Hand Stamp
Children 12 and under are free. Children are allowed in the VIP tent if accompanied by a parent or guardian.
Festival Gate Hours
Friday, Feb. 13: 5pm – 10pm
Saturday, Feb. 14: Noon – 10pm
Sunday, Feb. 15: Noon – 5pm
Use the form below to contact our team.
